      "content": "I'm not sure what you mean by \"goblins\" or \"elves\" in this context. I just need a professional analysis of the logistical causes for these variances. Can you stick to the technical possibilities like unit of measure errors, scanning glitches, or shrinkage? What are the most likely operational reasons for these specific numbers?",
